OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWhite House wants Moon to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhave its own time zone     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The White House wants US space agency  
OL,6, Nasa to develop a new time zone for the
OL,7, Moon - Coordinated Lunar Time (CLT).   
OL,9,FBecause of the different gravitational 
OL,10,Ffield strength on the Moon, time moves 
OL,11,Fquicker there relative to Earth - 58.7 
OL,12,Fmicroseconds every day.                
OL,14,FThis might not seem like much, but it  
OL,15,Fcan have a significant impact when     
OL,16,Ftrying to synchronise spacecraft.      
OL,18,FThe US government hopes the new time   
OL,19,Fwill help keep national and private    
OL,20,Fefforts to reach the moon co-ordinated.
